title: The Supreme Crazy Son-in-Law
summary: Zhi Zun Kuang Xu, 至尊狂婿 , Extreme mad son-in-law The Supreme Crazy Son-in-Law – The originally foolish Jiang Chen was forced to marry into one the Gu family because his birthday horoscope could cure Miss Gu’s illness. Unexpectedly, due to an accident, Jiang Chen, who was almost killed by the Gu family, possessed the soul and memories of a god-level celestial being…
